## 完整 lifecycle
```vue
<script setup>
import {
  onBeforeMount,
  onMounted,
  onBeforeUpdate,
  onUpdated,
  onBeforeUnmount,
  onUnmounted,
  onErrorCaptured,
} from "vue";

onBeforeMount(() => {
  console.log("元件還沒插入 DOM");
});

onMounted(() => {
  console.log("元件插入 DOM、可訪問 ref");
});

onBeforeUpdate(() => {
  console.log("資料變了、DOM 還沒更新");
});

onUpdated(() => {
  console.log("DOM 更新完");
});

onBeforeUnmount(() => {
  console.log("元件要消失了、清理時機");
});

onUnmounted(() => {
  console.log("元件消失");
});

onErrorCaptured((err) => {
  console.log("子元件錯誤:", err);
  return false;  // 阻止向上傳遞
});
</script>
```

## 常見用法

### onMounted: 抓資料
```javascript
import { onMounted, ref } from "vue";

const data = ref(null);

onMounted(async () => {
  const res = await fetch("/api/data");
  data.value = await res.json();
});
```

### onMounted: 註冊事件
```javascript
import { onMounted, onUnmounted } from "vue";

function handleScroll() { ... }

onMounted(() => {
  window.addEventListener("scroll", handleScroll);
});

onUnmounted(() => {
  window.removeEventListener("scroll", handleScroll);  // 清理
});
```

### onMounted: 拿 DOM ref
```vue
<script setup>
import { ref, onMounted } from "vue";

const inputRef = ref(null);

onMounted(() => {
  inputRef.value.focus();  // 自動聚焦
});
</script>

<template>
  <input ref="inputRef">
</template>
```

### onErrorCaptured: 錯誤邊界
```javascript
onErrorCaptured((err, instance, info) => {
  console.error("子元件 crash:", err);
  // 通知 Sentry
  return false;  // 不要傳遞
});
```

## SSR 注意
- `onMounted` 只在 client 跑
- `onBeforeMount` 也是 client only
- server side 只跑 `setup`

→ 用 `window` / DOM 必須在 onMounted 內：
```javascript
// ❌ 錯（SSR 會炸）
const width = window.innerWidth;

// ✅ 對
const width = ref(0);
onMounted(() => {
  width.value = window.innerWidth;
});
```

## 跟 React useEffect 對比
```
React:                  Vue:
useEffect(() => {}, [])   onMounted
useEffect(() => {})        watchEffect
useEffect cleanup          onUnmounted
useLayoutEffect            (沒直接對應、用 nextTick)
```

**☕ 用人話講**

元件生命週期＝元件從出現到消失之間的各個時間點。最常用 **onMounted**（畫面顯示後抓資料、拿 DOM、註冊事件），還有 **onErrorCaptured** 當錯誤邊界。**一句話記住**：像店面的營業流程——開門（mounted）擺貨、打烊（unmounted）收攤，在對的時段做對的事，程式才不會亂。

